<div id="Idea_2577"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2577-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2577">8 Open Government Data Principles&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">johnwonderlich</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The eight Open Government Data Principles should be implemented, making all government data: complete, primary, timely, accessible, machine processable, non-discriminatory, non-proprietary, and license-free. (see: http://resource.org/8_principles.html)</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2577" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2577', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=2577')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2577"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=principes">principes</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=malamud">malamud</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=sunlight">sunlight</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2577"></div>
